lead_paragraph: Rowdy Gaines clearly had much to say as Michael Phelps turned the race for his 22nd Olympic gold medal into a rout on Thursday. We're just not sure what it was.

headline.main: Who's More Excited: Michael Phelps or Rowdy Gaines?
